fields.name: Red Rose
fields.description: Red roses mean love and are also an expression of longing. Very nice between loving couples and in some cases between family members. Red is love and passion!

fields.name: Pink Rose
fields.description: Pink roses are used to show soft emotions such as admiration, joy and gratitude. Pink roses are often used when you want to show someone your gratitude and appreciation.

fields.name: White Rose
fields.description: White roses mean innocence, purity and chastity. The white rose often symbolizes a new beginning and is used when you want to communicate sympathy and humility.

fields.name: Bouquet of pink roses
fields.description: 1 rose tells the person that he or she is everything to you. 2 roses means that you would like to travel with the person who receives the bouquet. 3 roses is the same as saying you want to see each other again, maybe another date. 4 roses say that you appreciate the presence of the person who received the flowers.

fields.name: Nature Flowers
fields.description: The bouquet is inspired by autumn's warm colors and gives the bouquet plenty of colorful contrasts. The bouquet consists of a nice mix of sustainable flowers - the dark green Eucalyptus Parvi, the orange and lush Amaranthus, nice orange Andre Kirse, Ca√±a Hojas Brun and the nice orange flower Gypsophila, Trifle and Typha Mini Natur.

fields.name: Bouquet of tulips
fields.description: We want to inspire with beautiful tulips that perk up in anticipation of spring's warmth

fields.name: Vintage Summer Flowers Bouquet
fields.description: Vibrant, hardy and easy-to-grow summer flowers for fresh bouquets are cornflower, marigold, snapdragon, summer aster, collard green, clarkia, summer mallow, brush carnation, sunflower, sweet pea, zinnia, rosehip, primrose, maidenhair tree, dew salvia and summer rudbeckia.

fields.name: Free Vector Flowers
fields.description: The white, stylish bridal bouquet with some gold details that feels both simple and exclusive.

fields.name: Gloxinia has soft, fluffy leaves and bell-shaped single or double flowers. The flowers have a beautiful sheen on the surface that gives a feeling of velvet.
